Q12.  If you had a bacon() feature in a spam module, what would you call it after importing spam?

Ans. bacon() function is not exist yet, as per question. 

Q13.  What can you do to save a programme from crashing if it encounters an error?

Ans. error handeling: we will rectify that error to prevent from program crashing. 

Q14. What is the purpose of the try clause? What is the purpose of the except clause?

Ans. Try clause  test a block of code for error and the except clause handle the error. 
